{"tid":398903,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一名中國藉男子涉嫌於澳洲參與當地華人愛國活動\"坎培拉中國心\"時露械被捕","createTime":"2017-09-13T13:57:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T11:34:18.000Z","uid":63669,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"407f951a3b5424ee8780a31fc6be0781f3aa4a8f","tid":398903,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T13:57:56.000Z","msg":"[本報訊]<br />\n<br />\n一名中國藉男子涉嫌於澳洲參與當地華人愛國活動&quot;坎培拉中國心&quot;時露械被捕，並準備遣返中國。<br />\n<br />\n據消息指，該名中國藉男子名為陳雲根，參與活動時情緒激動，突然露出下體，上面刻有&quot;中國人&quot;三個字，並且不斷將其搖擺。<br />\n<br />\n記者其後調查發現，該男子與大紀元有緊密關係，本報向有關機構查詢後，負責人李洪志表示遺憾，並指會調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n類似的事件亦經常出現在各地，為當地人添加煩惱。雪梨的當地居民指，希望警方於相關的活動加派人手維持治安，亦表示華人的愛國活動為附近居民帶來煩惱。"},{"pid":"86a302f6314e356801d91fe54e0ea750b838bae3","tid":398903,"uid":109743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:40:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e0d1d6eab23e557f1381a648d8ce75460ca14e0","tid":398903,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T18:44:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9580a3610b9b1e0efa18110e67ffc41d8d5817b","tid":398903,"uid":48514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T18:48:44.000Z","msg":"搖撚凖備"},{"pid":"75f9e1f1a4b8cfe07c360095e724847541f4d40b","tid":398903,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T18:54:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5317eba52c7ad7ccdb27707306dc3a262760c644","tid":398903,"uid":33736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T18:58:00.000Z","msg":"陳雲根<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass